    {
      "question": "AipuPower ModuleIsolation Voltageetc.级has哪些？",
      "answer": "AipuPower Module提供多种Isolation Voltageetc.级以满足不同Application需求：1) 1000VDC：基础Isolationetc.级，适用于一般Industrial ControlApplication；2) 1500VDC：StandardIsolationetc.级，适用于大多数工业andCommunication Equipment；3) 2500VDC：高Isolationetc.级，适用于Power Systems、Medical Equipmentetc.forIsolation要求较高场合；4) 3000VDC：超高Isolationetc.级，适用于高压电力设备、医疗监护设备etc.特殊Application。Isolated Transceiver Module通常提供2500VDCIsolation Voltage。Selection时需考虑系统工作Voltage、安全要求andApplication环境。",
      "decisionGuide": "一般工业Application选1500VDC，电力and医疗Application选2500VDCor3000VDC。",
