      "faqs": [
        {
          "question": "什么isIsolated Transceiver？",
          "answer": "Isolated Transceiveris集成Power SupplyIsolationand信号Isolation通信接口模块。传统收发器需要外部IsolationPower Supplyand光耦/数字Isolation器实现Isolation，电路复杂。Isolated Transceiver将IsolationPower Supply、Isolation驱动器、收发器芯片集成in一个模块内，用户只需ConnectionPower Supply、信号线and总线即可。优势：1) 简化Design，节省PCB空间；2) 高Isolation Voltage（通常2500VDC）；3) 高共模抑制能力；4) Protection设备免受地环路干扰and高压瞬态损坏。",
          "decisionGuide": "需要电气Isolation通信接口首选Isolated Transceiver，简化Design提高Reliability。",
