            "Isolated Transceiver",
            "Power SupplyIsolation",
            "信号Isolation"
          ]
        },
        {
          "question": "AipuIsolated Transceiverhas哪些协议Support？",
          "answer": "AipuIsolated TransceiverSupport主流工业通信协议：1) CAN总线：CTM系列，SupportCAN2.0A/B协议，波特率最高1Mbps，符合ISO 11898Standard；2) RS-485：RSM系列，Support最高500Kbps波特率，符合TIA/EIA-485Standard，Support自动流控；3) RS-232：RSM232系列，Support最高115.2Kbps波特率，符合TIA/EIA-232Standard。所has系列均提供2500VDCIsolation Voltage，集成IsolationPower Supply，无需外部IsolationPower Supply。",
          "decisionGuide": "CAN总线选CTM系列，RS-485选RSM系列，RS-232选RSM232系列。",
          "keywords": [
            "CAN总线",
            "RS-485",
            "RS-232",
            "通信协议"
          ]
        },
        {
          "question": "Isolated TransceiverIsolation Voltageis多少？",
          "answer": "AipuIsolated Transceiver提供2500VDCIsolation Voltage，这is指Input侧（逻辑侧）andOutput侧（总线侧）之间可以承受2500VDCVoltage而不击穿。2500VDCIsolationetc.级适用于大多数工业Application，能够has效防止：1) 地环路干扰；2) 共模Voltage损坏；3) 高压瞬态（如雷电、开关浪涌）。Isolation VoltageTesting条件：Testing时间60秒，漏Current小于1mA。实际Isolation能BeiLuo常更高，典型击穿Voltage超过4000VDC。",
          "decisionGuide": "2500VDCIsolation适合大多数工业Application，Power Systems可能需要更高Isolationetc.级。",
